    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 requirements table. The validation evidence demonstrates that the CFD hemolysis model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment team accepts this UoA as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
